| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7434 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1f2205ec-a97e-5812-8ad4-b7a5c2ff4b69"
